item.title: About
item.description: A fan of new technologies, especially artificial intelligence and machine learning. Projects Fish recognition API: Sea fish classifier. Model developed with a RESNET 34 architecture with FastaAI2, Pytorch and Streamlite. The accuracy of the model in training was 7%. For the training of the model 44,134 images were used, which were scraped from the Internet. EngineEconomics: Library developed in Python to solve typical problems in Engineering Economics, Finance, and Project Evaluation.
